<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Apache Dubbo – 环境变量配置手册</title><link>https://dubbo.apache.org/zh/docs3-building/java-sdk/reference-manual/config/env/</link><description>Recent content in 环境变量配置手册 on Apache Dubbo</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><atom:link href="https://dubbo.apache.org/zh/docs3-building/java-sdk/reference-manual/config/env/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Docs3-Building: 配置指南</title><link>https://dubbo.apache.org/zh/docs3-building/java-sdk/reference-manual/config/env/guide/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://dubbo.apache.org/zh/docs3-building/java-sdk/reference-manual/config/env/guide/</guid><description>
&lt;p>从 2.7.3 版本开始，Dubbo 会自动从约定 key 中读取配置，并将配置以 Key-Value 的形式写入到URL中。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>支持的 key 有以下两个：&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>&lt;code>dubbo.labels&lt;/code>，指定一些列配置到 URL 中的键值对，通常通过 JVM -D 或系统环境变量指定。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>增加以下配置：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#93a1a1;background-color:#002b36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span># JVM
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>-Ddubbo.labels = &amp;#34;tag1=value1; tag2=value2&amp;#34;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span># 环境变量
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>DUBBO_LABELS = &amp;#34;tag1=value1; tag2=value2&amp;#34;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>最终生成的 URL 会包含 tag1、tag2 两个 key: &lt;code>dubbo://xxx?tag1=value1&amp;amp;tag2=value2&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>&lt;code>dubbo.env.keys&lt;/code>，指定环境变量 key 值，Dubbo 会尝试从环境变量加载每个 key&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#93a1a1;background-color:#002b36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span># JVM
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>-Ddubbo.env.keys = &amp;#34;DUBBO_TAG1, DUBBO_TAG2&amp;#34;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span># 环境变量
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>DUBBO_ENV_KEYS = &amp;#34;DUBBO_TAG1, DUBBO_TAG2&amp;#34;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>最终生成的 URL 会包含 DUBBO_TAG1、DUBBO_TAG2 两个 key: &lt;code>dubbo://xxx?DUBBO_TAG1=value1&amp;amp;DUBBO_TAG2=value2&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol></description></item><item><title>Docs3-Building: 配置项描述</title><link>https://dubbo.apache.org/zh/docs3-building/java-sdk/reference-manual/config/env/description/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://dubbo.apache.org/zh/docs3-building/java-sdk/reference-manual/config/env/description/</guid><description/></item></channel></rss>